narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Master-care INC is a Supports Brokerage provider based in Folsom, CA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $26.6M in Medicaid payments across 139K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $26.6M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
